U||   star-shadows—blotting them out as non-entities from the perception of
U||   the angels.
U||   P. You say that “but for the necessity of the rudimental life” there
U||   would have been no stars. But why this necessity?
U||   V. In the inorganic life, as well as in the inorganic matter generally,
