U||   the windows, and down the staircases of the Ducal Palace, turned all at
U||   once that deep gloom into a livid and preternatural day.
U||   A child, slipping from the arms of its own mother, had fallen from an
U||   upper window of the lofty structure into the deep and dim canal. The
U||   quiet waters had closed placidly over their victim; and, although my
U||   own gondola was the only one in sight, many a stout swimmer, already in
U||   the stream, was seeking in vain upon the surface, the treasure which
U||   was to be found, alas! only within the abyss. Upon the broad black
U||   marble flagstones at the entrance of the palace, and a few steps above
