U||   She stood alone. Her small, bare, and silvery feet gleamed in the black
U||   mirror of marble beneath her. Her hair, not as yet more than half
U||   loosened for the night from its ball-room array, clustered, amid a
U||   shower of diamonds, round and round her classical head, in curls like
