U||   whose name the greater part of Europe was then ringing.
U||   No word spoke the deliverer. But the Marchesa! She will now receive her
U||   child—she will press it to her heart—she will cling to its little form,
U||   and smother it with her caresses. Alas! another’s arms have taken it
U||   from the stranger—another’s arms have taken it away, and borne it afar
