U||   decora of what is technically called keeping, or to the proprieties of
U||   nationality. The eye wandered from object to object, and rested upon
U||   none—neither the grotesques of the Greek painters, nor the sculptures
U||   of the best Italian days, nor the huge carvings of untutored Egypt.
U||   Rich draperies in every part of the room trembled to the vibration of
